                    "RegionId": "CN4206",
                    "Title": "襄阳",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"235370c7fa5e45329b23a6a4b2919c71\");'><span id='235370c7fa5e45329b23a6a4b2919c71_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=800&endYear=801')\">800-801年</a>，21-22岁</div><div id='235370c7fa5e45329b23a6a4b2919c71' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=800&endYear=800')\">800年</a>　开始外出游学，干谒名流。于本年前后赴襄阳拜谒山南东道节度使于頔，不为所礼，怒而去。外出游学、干谒名流过程中，撰写了传奇集《玄怪录》中的部分篇章。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=801&endYear=801')\">801年</a>　拜谒山南东道节度使于頔未受礼遇，可能在江、黄一代游学。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7125d1a1207641549d3f8aa6e5209220\");'><span id='7125d1a1207641549d3f8aa6e5209220_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=825&endYear=825')\">825年</a>，46岁</div><div id='7125d1a1207641549d3f8aa6e5209220' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=825&endYear=825')\">825年</a>　牛僧孺出为武昌军节度使，途经襄州，山南东道节度使柳公绰隆礼相迎。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1d3fb19fb3b44df19e7e6311d4fff5f7\");'><span id='1d3fb19fb3b44df19e7e6311d4fff5f7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=839&endYear=841')\">839-841年</a>，60-62岁</div><div id='1d3fb19fb3b44df19e7e6311d4fff5f7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=839&endYear=839')\">839年</a>　本年八月，牛僧孺以使相身份出镇山南东道。牛僧孺在襄州辟刘蕡为幕僚，辟卢简求为使府观察判官，辟韩愈子韩昶为使府殿中侍御史加观察支使。本年，牛僧孺与白居易、刘禹锡继续有诗歌唱和。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=840&endYear=840')\">840年</a>　本年，牛僧孺夫人辛氏卒。在襄州，牛僧孺与释思公（僧思公）有交往。本年，分司东都的太子宾客白居易仍有诗寄牛僧孺。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=841&endYear=841')\">841年</a>　九月前，牛僧孺依旧以使相身份任职山南东道节度使。<br /></div>"
                },
                {
                    "Latitude": 34.624376,
                    "Longitude": 112.460033,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN4103",
                    "Title": "洛阳",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8f9a7a2357cf47568558a275812beb90\");'><span id='8f9a7a2357cf47568558a275812beb90_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=807&endYear=807')\">807年</a>，28岁</div><div id='8f9a7a2357cf47568558a275812beb90' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=807&endYear=807')\">807年</a>　于今年或去年释褐为伊阙县尉。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f2ed2060ac92483787dbacdde9d8c088\");'><span id='f2ed2060ac92483787dbacdde9d8c088_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=808&endYear=813')\">808-813年</a>，29-34岁</div><div id='f2ed2060ac92483787dbacdde9d8c088' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=808&endYear=808')\">808年3月</a>　三月，诏举贤良方正能直言极谏科，牛僧孺等直陈时政，得罪权贵，宰相李吉甫恶其直言，牛僧孺赴河南尹杜兼幕任水路运判官，兼任伊阙县尉。本年，牛僧孺在洛阳初识殿中侍御史分司东都韦乾度，并再次与韩愈相会。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=809&endYear=809')\">809年9月23日</a>　牛僧孺在河南尹杜兼幕任水路运判官，兼任伊阙县尉。九月二十三日，牛僧孺与韩愈、李宗闵于洛阳福先寺迎候杜兼，并题名于福先寺塔。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=810&endYear=810')\">810年</a>　牛僧孺告诫好友白居易谨慎行事以免祸。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=811&endYear=811')\">811年</a>　牛僧孺与辛秘之女结婚。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=812&endYear=812')\">812年</a>　牛僧孺约于本年除河南尉。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=813&endYear=813')\">813年</a>　牛僧孺仍为河南尉。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"537bfeadb1e846d5a03cf99479fdc014\");'><span id='537bfeadb1e846d5a03cf99479fdc014_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=833&endYear=833')\">833年</a>，54岁</div><div id='537bfeadb1e846d5a03cf99479fdc014' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=833&endYear=833')\">833年</a>　早春，牛僧孺在赴淮南途中与太子宾客分司洛阳的白居易相会于洛阳。本年春，牛僧孺抵达淮南。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8d8e1d0547b742898efe96bb7e6d0a0d\");'><span id='8d8e1d0547b742898efe96bb7e6d0a0d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=837&endYear=838')\">837-838年</a>，58-59岁</div><div id='8d8e1d0547b742898efe96bb7e6d0a0d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=837&endYear=837')\">837年</a>　本年初牛僧孺累求罢淮南重镇之职，五月，获准罢镇，改授东都留守。牛僧孺卸任淮南，李德裕代之，诬奏牛僧孺副使张鹭侵吞公款，以中伤牛僧孺。牛僧孺在洛阳居于归仁里，并在南郊营建“南庄”别墅。牛僧孺任东都留守后，苏州刺史李道枢赠其太湖石，牛僧孺、白居易、刘禹锡均有诗咏此事。牛僧孺任东都留守时，曾一度悠闲服食，与白居易、刘禹锡多有诗歌唱和，然牛诗皆佚。本年，牛僧孺次子牛丛与李商隐等东登进士第，外孙苗台符出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=838&endYear=838')\">838年</a>　本年九月前，仍任职东都留守。本年九月，文宗遣使征牛僧孺入朝为左仆射，牛僧孺赴长安途中，至甘棠馆梦与刘禹锡携手同游，遂有诗互赠。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f3f203a9b1ef40aeaae354525264c6fa\");'><span id='f3f203a9b1ef40aeaae354525264c6fa_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=842&endYear=844')\">842-844年</a>，63-65岁</div><div id='f3f203a9b1ef40aeaae354525264c6fa' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=842&endYear=842')\">842年</a>　十二月，牛僧孺等奏上《升御史大夫为三品奏》。同时，牛僧孺等又上《改谏议大夫为正四品下奏》。年底，牛僧孺出为检校司徒、太子太傅、东都留守。在洛阳，牛僧孺与以刑部尚书分司致仕的白居易有诗歌唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《改谏议大夫为正四品下奏》<span class='inlineComment2'>（《改谏议大夫为正四品下奏》，见《唐会要》卷五十五。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=843&endYear=843')\">843年</a>　三月，李德裕追论维州事，旨在委罪于牛僧孺，会泽潞事起，暂缓。五月，白居易为牛僧孺撰《太湖石记》。本年白居易仍与牛僧孺多有诗歌往来。本年，牛僧孺黜降留守府讨击使张季戎为衙前将。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=844&endYear=844')\">844年</a>　十月，李德裕因泽潞事，罗织罪名，诬奏牛僧孺、李宗闵、刘从谏等，贬牛僧孺为太子少保分司，李宗闵为漳州刺史。不久，再贬牛僧孺为汀州刺史，李宗闵为漳州长史。十一月，复贬牛僧孺为循州长史，李宗闵长流封州。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"43fde6b2136642d48ec1c62f6a0df1b4\");'><span id='43fde6b2136642d48ec1c62f6a0df1b4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=848&endYear=848')\">848年</a>，69岁</div><div id='43fde6b2136642d48ec1c62f6a0df1b4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=848&endYear=848')\">848年</a>　夏秋之际，牛僧孺由汝州长史迁太子少保分司东都，复迁太子少师。十月，卒于洛阳，册赠太尉。后于大中十三年赐谥号曰“文贞”<br /></div>"
                },
                {
                    "Latitude": 30.598428,
                    "Longitude": 114.311831,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN4201",
                    "Title": "武汉",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"04236ff903b644c7889ce36069fece35\");'><span id='04236ff903b644c7889ce36069fece35_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=825&endYear=829')\">825-829年</a>，46-50岁</div><div id='04236ff903b644c7889ce36069fece35' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=825&endYear=825')\">825年</a>　牛僧孺镇武昌，辟李珏、柳仲郢、韩佽为幕府从事。牛僧孺赴任伊始，即革除弊政，解除州人筑城之劳。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=826&endYear=826')\">826年</a>　四月，牛僧孺奏请省并管内州县，以裁减冗官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=827&endYear=827')\">827年</a>　牛僧孺奏题释无等兰若曰“大寂院”。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=828&endYear=828')\">828年</a>　仍在武昌节度使任，为崔群撰家庙碑。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《崔群家庙碑》<span class='inlineComment2'>（《崔群家庙碑》见于《全唐文》卷六八二。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=828&endYear=828')\">828年</a>　秋，编录《玄怪录·齐饶州》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=829&endYear=829')\">829年</a>　仍在武昌节度使任，由检校礼部尚书加检校吏部尚书。于武昌拜会道士“毛仙翁”。后作《别志》纪其事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《别志》<span class='inlineComment2'>（《别志》见于《全唐文》卷六八二。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=829&endYear=829')\">829年</a>　仍在武昌节度使任，由检校礼部尚书加检校吏部尚书。本年撰《赠吏部尚书杨玄琰碑》<span class='label'>作品：</span>《赠吏部尚书杨玄琰碑》<span class='inlineComment2'>（牛僧孺撰《赠吏部尚书杨玄琰碑》，见于《宝刻丛编》卷八。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=829&endYear=829')\">829年</a>　仍在武昌节度使任，由检校礼部尚书加检校吏部尚书。本年编录《玄怪录·尼妙寂》<br /></div>"
                },
                {
                    "Latitude": 32.39986,
                    "Longitude": 119.419107,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN321",
                    "Title": "扬州",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a8cae14ed9614dd5b4b90b3592c17223\");'><span id='a8cae14ed9614dd5b4b90b3592c17223_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=833&endYear=837')\">833-837年</a>，54-58岁</div><div id='a8cae14ed9614dd5b4b90b3592c17223' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=833&endYear=833')\">833年</a>　本年春，牛僧孺抵达淮南。杜牧奉宣歙观察使沈传师之命，赴扬州拜访牛僧孺。四月，牛僧孺辟杜牧为淮南节度府掌书记。本年秋，李绅由洛阳赴浙东观察使任，途中与牛僧孺会于扬州。本年前后，牛僧孺为温造父温辅国撰神道碑。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《唐谏议大夫温府君碑》<span class='inlineComment2'>（牛僧孺撰《唐谏议大夫温府君碑》，见《宝刻丛编》卷四，又见《唐文拾遗》卷二七。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=834&endYear=834')\">834年</a>　本年，杜牧仍在牛僧孺淮南节度使任幕僚，杜牧生活放浪，牛僧孺对其备极关怀。本年秋，刘禹锡由苏州刺史移汝州刺史，途经扬州，与牛僧孺会面，有诗唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《席上赠刘梦得》<span class='inlineComment2'>（《席上赠刘梦得》，见《全唐诗》卷四百六十六。《云溪友议》载该诗名《席上赠汝州刘中丞》）</span><div id='poem_7724' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_7724' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=7724' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>席上赠刘梦得</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(18505, \"唐\", \"牛僧孺\", \"poem_title_7724\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 唐·</span>牛僧孺</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_7724_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_7724'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_7724'><span class='link' onclick='ShowWordComment(\"poem_sentence_0_7724\", 7724, \"Clauses/0/Comments/0\")'>粉署</span>为郎四十春，今来<span class='link' onclick='ShowWordComment(\"poem_sentence_0_7724\", 7724, \"Clauses/1/Comments/0\")'>名辈</span>更无人。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_7724_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_7724'>休论世上<span class='link' onclick='ShowWordComment(\"poem_sentence_1_7724\", 7724, \"Clauses/2/Comments/0\")'>升沉</span>事，且斗樽前<span class='link' onclick='ShowWordComment(\"poem_sentence_1_7724\", 7724, \"Clauses/3/Comments/0\")'>见在身</span>。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_7724_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_7724'>珠玉会应成咳唾，山川犹觉露精神。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_7724_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_7724'>莫嫌恃酒轻言语，曾把文章<span class='link' onclick='ShowWordComment(\"poem_sentence_3_7724\", 7724, \"Clauses/7/Comments/0\")'>谒后尘</span>。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_7724_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_7724'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_7724_comment'></div></div><div class='poemComment' id='poem_comment_7724'><a href='javascript: ShowPoemComment(7724)'>评注</a><span class='inlineComment4'>（点击查看或隐藏评注）</span></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=835&endYear=835')\">835年</a>　本年五月，李绅由浙东观察使改任太子宾客，分司东都，经扬州，再次与牛僧孺相会。本年，杜牧擢监察御史，离开牛僧孺淮南幕府，赴长安供职，不久移疾，分司东都。本年冬，牛僧孺辟杜牧弟杜顗入幕府，顗辞谢不就。本年秋，李党人物托名刘轲作《牛羊日历》，极力诽谤牛僧孺等。本年，牛僧孺长子牛蔚登进士科。本年或去年，牛僧孺外孙张读出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=836&endYear=836')\">836年</a>　本年，牛僧孺仍在淮南节度使任，与白居易有诗歌唱和与礼物互赠。李德裕亲信韦瓘可能于本年伪托牛僧孺作《周秦行纪》，诬陷牛僧孺，赖文宗明察，未能得逞。本年，“《周秦行纪》案”后，牛僧孺厌倦了党争，累表求罢归散地，未获许。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=837&endYear=837')\">837年</a>　由于受到“《周秦行纪》案”的影响，本年初牛僧孺累求罢淮南重镇之职，五月，获准罢镇，改授东都留守。<br /></div>"
                },
                {
