                    "Longitude": 114.423348,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN4413",
                    "Title": "惠州",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7f5489edd3f64d12ac5f8a6fbc47361b\");'><span id='7f5489edd3f64d12ac5f8a6fbc47361b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=844&endYear=846')\">844-846年</a>，65-67岁</div><div id='7f5489edd3f64d12ac5f8a6fbc47361b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=844&endYear=844')\">844年10月</a>　十月，牛僧孺因泽潞事被贬循州长史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=845&endYear=845')\">845年</a>　二月，素被牛僧孺器重的柳仲郢为李德裕引荐为京兆尹。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=846&endYear=846')\">846年</a>　春，牛僧孺仍在循州，白居易有诗怀之。八月，牛僧孺与李宗闵、崔珙、杨嗣复、李珏等被诏北迁，牛僧孺由循州长史移衡州长史。<br /></div>"
